<br>
&quot;Rogue Centaurs.&quot;<br>
<br>
She glanced back at Zelia.<br>
<br>
&quot;Perhaps you can pay back the Nation from what was taken from it.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uiizeliaii.showPublicProfile?language=EN>II Zelia II</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 138<br> <font color=#993300>(8/18/02 10:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=377.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re:</span><hr size=1> Peeks thru the bushes aswell,looking at the rogue centaurs.<br>
<br>
