<br>
She fixes her gaze on Alysia.<br>
<br>
&quot;Wha-&quot;<br>
<br>
She took a long moment to think.<br>
<br>
&quot;Well I never.&quot; She huffs,then retracts her impalers.<br>
<br>
&quot;That was just a test? I havn't taken a test in a long time,you could have warned me,so I could have studied.&quot; Grunts.<br>
